      <title>陷入困境的矿工阻碍了南非股市的上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/struggling-miners-put-the-brakes-on-south-africa-s-stock-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非股市在新兴市场股市中处于领先地位，但来自中国的低迷消息可能会给关键的采矿业带来压力，并阻碍其优异表现。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/struggling-miners-put-the-brakes-on-south-africa-s-stock-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 05:43:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>IEEFA 称欧洲液化天然气产量达到峰值，搁浅资产风险加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/europe-at-peak-lng-heightens-risk-of-stranded-assets-ieefa-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家能源智库表示，欧洲液化天然气消费量可能已达到峰值，但仍在继续建设进口终端和相关基础设施，这增加了这些工程闲置并成为搁浅资产的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/europe-at-peak-lng-heightens-risk-of-stranded-assets-ieefa-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行将降息但仍对未来路径持谨慎态度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/ecb-interest-rates-decision-lagarde-to-cut-but-stay-guarded-on-future</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行将再次下调利率，但由于通胀尚未完全得到抑制，其对进一步行动的速度和程度仍守口如瓶。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/ecb-interest-rates-decision-lagarde-to-cut-but-stay-guarded-on-future</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
